{
  "texts": [
    "The effectiveness of the proposed semantic similarity measures in enhancing the performance of item-based CF is investigated.",
    "The evaluation involves three key comparison scenarios.",
    "First, we individually evaluate the influence of each semantic similarity measure on the recommendation accuracy in conjunction with the item-based CF approach, and the obtained results are analyzed.",
    "Second, we examine the impact of the proposed Fusion-based SS measure on recommendation accuracy when used alongside item-based CF.",
    "Finally, we investigate the highest recommendation accuracy attained by the aforementioned experimental scenarios relative to other benchmark methods, focusing on predictive accuracy, sparsity, and new item problems."
  ]
}